The Berlinale Film Festival is currently going on in the German capital, so everything at Euromaxx this week is also focused on the world of film. What movie genres do you like to watch most? Are you a fan of romance? Action? Perhaps science fiction? Let us know what kinds of films you enjoy! It’s easy to take part. Just click on one of the choices below and briefly explain why that genre is your favorite.  As a thank-you, we’ll be drawing from among all of the entrants, and one lucky contestant will receive a wristwatch in an exclusive Euromaxx design. Drama Comedy Romance Crime/Thriller Horror Science Fiction Action Documentary Telenovela Bollywood The closing date for entries is February 23, 2018, (12:00 UTC). Our decision is final. Best of luck!